creator: Rising Products
descriptionHtml:
Landmark is an Informational and Utility Service Dedicated to the Member of Dhanera and Khimat Jain Samaj. Started on 2nd June 2012 with a Novel Idea of Broadcasting Sad News among the Community Members to avoid Individual Phone calls to each and every Member. Gradually several Services have been added. The Services now include:

1. News: Broadcasting Sad News, Good News, Educational Success News, Charity News, Sports News, Sangh News and General, Important and Landmark News.

2. Darshika: An Online Vasti Patrak of Dhanera and Khimat Jain Samaj updated regularly.

3. Melap: Matrimonial Information of all eligible Boys and Girls.

4. Vanita: A Promotional Platform for the benefit of Women Entrepreneurs of the Community.

5. Lifeline: A Complete Online Directory of Blood Donors with their Blood Group information.

6. Directory: A Phone Book of all the members of the Community.

All these services were being provided by Landmark with the help of it Mobile Application “Telex Landmark”. In association of Dhanera Sahayog Trust we proudly present a New Version of the Application “Landmark Live” as on 25th February 2019 by adding New Services that are absolutely Necessary for the Upliftment of the Under Privileged members of the Community.

Following Services have been Added in the New Version of the Application:

1. Sahayog: A Service to support daily needs of the people, pension to the Senior Citizens to sustain a Life of Dignity.

2. Education: A Service with a Futuristic View to serve the Youth of Dhanera seeking Scholarship or Loan for Education.

3. Hostel: A Service to provide Accommodation to the Community Members coming to Mumbai for earning their livelihood.

We shall be adding more services in the near future.
